Package itunesq

Class Database

java.lang.Object
itunesq.Database
public final class Database extends Object
Class that contains the internal database in which tracks, playlists and artists are stored.

This is a final class consisting entirely of static methods.

Author:
Jon

      decrement - number of playlists contained in the folder added to the ignored list
